Sister Rosetta Tharpe: the GODMOTHER  of Rock’n’Roll “She could outplay Chuck. She could outsing Aretha. And she influenced everyone from Elvis to Rod.” (The Guardian) HAPPY WOMENSDAY TO EVERYBODY Let’s celebrate all women who fought for us to have what we got now. Unfortunately there is still a lot to be done... ...especially in the music scene: Women are massively underrepresented in the music industry. “more than two-thirds of the live music acts performing in the UK will feature no women on stage” (the Guardian) Also in Austria I am missing female instrumentalist in live acts. So grab your instruments and take your talents to the stage.  We need more role models like Sister Rosetta Tharpe 💪.
